description:
TERMS AND CONDITIONS

We glide rain or shine! Ponchos are provided. In the event of extreme inclement weather, as predicted by the National Weather Forecast Service, rain checks or rescheduling options are available. We require a minimum of 48 hours advance notice of your scheduled tour departure for all cancellations and rescheduling unless canceled by (Absolutely Chicago Segway Tours). Tours must depart at their scheduled departure time. Late arrivals will not be admitted and forfeit their payment. Any tour that is canceled or rescheduled less than 48 hours of scheduled departure is non-refundable. All cancellations are subject to an 8% processing cancellation fee unless canceled by (ACST).

Those persons who are under the influence of drugs or alcohol are not permitted to participate and a refund will not be issued. All participants must at least 14 years old, weight more than 100 pounds and less than 260 in accordance with manufacturer recommendations. Anyone under the age of 18 years old must be accompanied by an adult. Participants must be able to stand for extended periods of time. All participants must be able to ascend a flight of stairs without assistance. Pregnant women are prohibited from participating in this activity.

Any reservation of 6 or more will be charged a gratuity of 15% upon arrival. Any group of 8 or more that which desires to glide together is considered a private tour and is subject to a service charge and gratuity upon arrival. Please refer to all FAQ's for further stipulations and recommendations.

We do require all participants sign waivers and release forms absolving ABS LLC, all employees of ACST from any and all litigant and responsibility for any and all injury or damages as you glide at their own risk. We do provide training and practice.

description: Mike Shannon's Grill is the new upscale-casual eatery from the team behind downtown St. Louis' favorite steakhouse Mike Shannon's Steaks And Seafood. Mike Shannon's Grill has a vintage athletic club look accented with modern industrial design elements. The venue features old school leather booths, raised-wood paneling, repurposed gym lights as well as an open ceiling and 18 flat-screen TVs. Baseball memorabilia is a highlight of the venue decor but in a different manner than at the downtown steakhouse. The 5000-square foot bar and grill includes three distinct areas: a family-friendly dining room highlighted by the signature baseball wall, a high-energy bar area featuring a wraparound zinc bar with a 90" LCD display ideal for watching the game, and an outdoor patio area built around a central firepit that overlooks Plum Creek. Mike Shannon's Grill serves comfort cuisine appealing to a wide variety of customers and dining occasions. The beverage program includes approximately 40 wines, many available by the glass, a cocktail list with both classic and contemporary selections, and a wide sampling of beer, including 16 beers available on draft.

description: Giving someone a gift card ensures that they can get what they want for a birthday, a wedding, the winter holidays and other occasions. While gift card gifts are always appreciated, sometimes, you want to give someone more than just a simple piece of plastic for a special event. On those occasions, the TechTools Gift Card Maze is the perfect way to add fun to your gift!

The TechTools Gift Card Maze is a gift card holder unlike anything you've seen before. Not a sleeve or a folder, this gift card holder is a clear plastic vault with a puzzle maze inside. In order to open the gift card maze and get to the gift card, the recipient of your gift first needs to turn the puzzle this way and that to roll the metal ball bearing to the other side! It's challenging yet simple enough for any adult or child to do successfully.

Measuring 5.5 inches by 3.5 inches in size, the TechTools Gift Card Maze is perfectly proportioned to hold all types of standard gift cards. You can also use the gift card maze for giving cash gifts in fun new ways! Once the gift card holder has been opened, it can be sealed again. Kids can play with the puzzle over and over, or the gift card maze can be reused to make another present extra special. The heavy-duty plastic construction ensures that the gift card holder will last for years to come.
Why give a plain old gift card when you can give someone special a gift card and a fun, memorable experience at the same time?
Choose the most unique gift card holder on Amazon!

description:
Cattle Baron Restaurants, Inc.is a privately held company founded in 1976 in Portales, New Mexico by the founder and CEO of the company, Jeff Wilson. Jeff Wilson Purchased "Bob's Steak House" upon completion of his service in the United States Air Force at Cannon Air Force Base in Clovis, New Mexico. Promptly he renamed the location to "Cattle Baron Steak & Seafood Restaurant". Jeff operated this location for eight years before embarking on a successful expansion program.

To date, Cattle Baron restaurants can be found in Hobbs, Roswell, Ruidoso and Las Cruces New Mexico; and in Lubbock, Midland and El Paso Texas. In 1995 in concept, Farley's Food Fun & Pub was established in Ruidoso, NM offering a more casual "sports bar" Atmosphere.
